Package edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.api.output

Record Class ArDoCoResult

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.api.output.ArDoCoResult
public record ArDoCoResult(edu.kit.kastel.informalin.data.DataRepository dataRepository) extends Record
This record represents the result of running ArDoCo. It is backed by a DataRepository and grabs data from it. Besides accessing all data from the calculation steps, this record also provides some convenience methods to directly access results such as found trace links and detected inconsistencies.
